entries.journal_entry_description: Deliver the contraband to the fence in the allotted time.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Kam in the allotted time.  For this assignment, you must avoid using any methods of travel other than on the ground, the authorities watch the travel terminals and shuttleports like hawks. A bounty has been placed on your head for accepting this assignment, so be on the look out. Do not be surprised if Kam is suspicious that you have been followed. He will only accept the merchandise when he feels comfortable it is safe.

entries.task05_comm_message_text: This is not good. I deal only with the best. If you cannot handle these assignments I will find someone else who can. Do not fail me again!
